> [quaint](#comment_2_1GNJvtrzvAKGPyShdbL2WSppKEbPrCFM87): I see none. You keep what you visit it seems?

Yes - even after you delete the folder the images and vids are still there.

> [quaint](#comment_1_1GNJvtrzvAKGPyShdbL2WSppKEbPrCFM87): didn't know zeronet stored whole files all the time? Should have read how that goes. Now I know where all my little disk space went.

Also, JPEGs show in browser history.
